1767
01:40:42,136 --> 01:40:43,706
Seus filhos da puta!

1768
01:40:48,642 --> 01:40:49,985
Levante-se, já!

1769
01:40:51,912 --> 01:40:53,419
- Mestre Jin Hyuk.  - Huh?

